- Grep for mutating patterns (new Task(, new Project(, .save(), markComplete(, remove) — zero matches in code examples
- Grep for read-only enforcement text
- Grep for query patterns (inbox, search, project, tags)
- Grep for JSON.stringify
- Grep for POST /eval instruction
- Write evidence to .ai/runs/$KILROY_RUN_ID/test-evidence/latest/IT-6/
- Start with #!/bin/sh, set -e, trap for KILROY_VALIDATE_FAILURE

